si.title: අ.පො.ස. උසස් පෙළ ශ්රේණි
body_lines: 2023 අධ්යාපන මධ්යස්ථානය පිළිබඳ අ.පො.ස. උසස් පෙළ විභාගයේ ප්රති results ල මේ වසරට පෙර නිකුත් කරන ලදී.

en.title: GCE Advanced Level Grades
body_lines: The results of the GCE Advanced Level Examination of the 2023 Education Center were released shortly before this year.

summary_lines: The 2023 GCE Advanced Level Examination results have been announced.
